# music_dailies
1. Make a video game bgm
2. Footage from a pre-existing video game OR movie with your own original music over the top. (E.g. you could mute some video footage of Super Mario and then write your own music over the top) credit: <https://www.reddit.com/r/gamedev/comments/p1jkpm/i_want_to_make_music_for_videogames_where_do_i/> good `[youtube video](youtube___20251212_1512_43.pd)` idea as well
